Description:
You arrive at a pallisade and find a couple of ratmen standing by some magical torches. One of them says:

"Interesting... if you are here it means you have entered through the crack and defeated the dead.

You see, I was one of the king's advisors... One of his rings saved him from freezing and then he managed to unfreeze some of us. But soon after, he made a deal with a dracomancer named Fred, and betrayed us all...
DescriptionAction: Well, that doesn't matter anymore, thanks to you we can go out. Can I do something for you?

    "SSRewardText": "(Ratman) \"Yes, I remember you... A few years after exiling you, the king became greedy and fearless of the elves.
